data.description: Welcome Home to 1230 Fenwick Rd:  Nestled in the heart of Aberdeen, MD, Its the perfect blend of modern comfort and suburban charm. This meticulously maintained home offers a serene retreat, as you approach, you'll be greeted by the inviting curb appeal. Step inside to discover a spacious and light-filled interior, The stylish kitchen has been upgraded, boasting sleek appliances, designer backsplash, ample cabinet space, and kitchen island.  The adjacent living area provides the perfect space for relaxation and entertainment, with its open layout and cozy atmosphere. Retreat to comfortable bedrooms, where plush carpeting and generous closet space provide a peaceful sanctuary for rest and relaxation. The well-appointed bathrooms feature modern fixtures and finishes, adding to the overall sense of luxury.  Outside, the backyard and the large composite deck offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, vinyl privacy fence/fenced in yard with gate and rain-guard to stay dry under deck, It's the perfect spot for summer barbecues. Located near shopping, dining, entertainment, and major commuter routes.   Additional features and upgrades include, full brick front/elevation, designer light fixtures throughout, energy-efficient rated home, RUCKUS hard-wired mesh wi-fi system delivers speed of up to 1GB per floor and finished garage.  Residents enjoy access to a plethora of amenities within the neighborhood, including picturesque walking trails, a refreshing community pool, well-maintained tennis courts, a fully equipped clubhouse boasting a gym, a versatile meeting space perfect for hosting gatherings, and an expansive playground for families to delight in.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home your own. $200/yr Front Foot and $140/yr Usage Fee.  Schedule a private tour today!
